videos.description: Syracuse's John Gillion drives the lane and goes up for a layup. He gets fouled and loses one of his shoes when he touches the ground.
videos.headline: Syracuse's GIllion loses shoe on layup attempt

videos.description: 1H (10:24) SYR Tyler Lydon made Two Point Tip Shot.
videos.headline: Tyler Lydon flies in from out of nowhere for the tip in

videos.description: Georgetown's L.J. Peak chases down Frank Howard and swats away the ball mid-dunk.
videos.headline: Georgetown's Peak thwarts dunk with chase down block

videos.description: At halftime of Syracuse's game against Georgetown, the Orange pay tribute to Dwayne "Pearl" Washington.
videos.headline: Syracuse honors 'Pearl' Washington with court dedication

videos.description: 2H (18:12) SYR Tyler Lydon made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Frank Howard.
videos.headline: Tyler Lydon drains a 3 and celebrates
Rodney Pryor misses a 3-pointer, dishes to Jessie Govan for the lay-in

videos.description: Georgetown's Rodney Pryor takes a pass from Tre Campbell and is fouled as he scores on a layup, extending the Hoyas' lead.
videos.headline: Georgetown's Pryor gets the basket for a layup and-1
